---
title: Golden Breaded Pork with Broccoli and Garlicky Mayo
description: Tender pork, wholesome broccoli and BBQ-spiced sweet potato wedges make a tasty trio for dunking into our yummy garlic dip. Everyone in the family is sure to love this easy weeknight meal.
